headline: Will Cigna (CI) Accelerate its Healthcare Innovation Narrative with Expanded AI Imaging Coverage?
summary: Cleerly announced that Cigna will begin covering Cleerly LABS' AI-powered Advanced Plaque Analysis for cardiovascular care as of October 1, 2025, making Cigna the latest major insurer to adopt AI-Enabled CT-based quantitative coronary tomography technology for patients meeting specific clinical criteria. This decision brings Cigna in line with other industry leaders and Medicare, contributing to rapid nationwide payor adoption of advanced AI-driven imaging technologies that aim to support...
